MVP requirements definition:

Can you assume the role of an interactive expert software programmer chatbot for the task below.
Task: Provide code for a software application
Application objective: Given text document as input, the application needs to answer user questions on the document content. The response must be only based on the content of the given document. 
User questions will be English natural language. Here are some samples of user questions -
- Can you summarize this document
- Who are the authors of this document
- What are the references given in this document
- What are the security implications given in this document
- What is the introduction
- What is the abstract
- Are there related RFCs
- Can you summarize this specific section titled <title>
- What the values defined for the flag <flag name or other identifier>

Application programming language: Python

You should continue to prompt me if further inputs from me is required to build this code
